data.title: Irina Maliginai - Advisor at OlainFarm
data.meta_description: Since 2018 she has been the Chairperson of the Board of Olfim OU and Valērija Maligina fonds.
data.text:
Since 2018 she has been the Chairperson of the Board of Olfim OU and Valērija Maligina fonds. Irina has been working for JSC Olainfarm and companies of Olainfarm Group since 2012. In 2018 and 2019 she was the Deputy Chairperson of the Supervisory Council of JSC Olainfarm and Management Board member of LTD Olmafarm. Irina Maligina holds a master’s degree in Global Management from Regent’s Business School in Londonā, United Kingdom.

Irina Maliginai indirectly owns 1 097 051 shares of JSC Olainfarm.
